title: Oh My Ears
info:
"I have titles to each section of this piece:

1. Fugue on an Over-Played Theme by Mozart
2. Mary Had a Little Bitonality
3. Rondo Alla Jerka
4. The Beauty of Twelve Tone Composition
5. The Lone Ranger Takes a Couple Falls
6. The Divorce March
7. Gargamel Ruins a Smurf Picnic
8. ...with a broken banjo on my knee...
9. Finale

Are your ears bleeding yet?

Those who think this didn't require any musical ability need to listen closer... :)" - note from the author
